flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B{Two pattern arguments?}
    B -- No --> C[Print usage and exit]
    B -- Yes --> D[Set rename counter to 0]
    D --> E[Loop through files matching old pattern]
    E --> F{Regular file?}
    F -- No --> K{More matches?}
    F -- Yes --> G[Strip path with basename]
    G --> H[Replace old pattern with new pattern]
    H --> I[Rename file with mv]
    I --> J[Increment counter]
    J --> K
    K -- Yes --> E
    K -- No --> L[Print files renamed]
    L --> M[Exit]
